    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS timing. This unit is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and the cooling system has been recently overhauled. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its mileage, the performance remains sharp with a linear power delivery to its 8,000 RPM redline. Suspension geometry is true, and the chassis remains stiff for spirited cornering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
