      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, showing only the minor road wear expected of a well-loved vehicle. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system\u2014functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recent multi-point inspection that included new brake pads and a fresh oil change. It drives straight, shifts effortlessly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
